Nick Stewart https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nick_Stewart 0 Horace Winfred "Nick" Stewart (March 15, 1910 – December 18, 2000) was an American television and film actor. Stewart was known for his role as Lightnin' (Willie Jefferson) on TV's The Amos 'n' Andy Show.
